{"tid":925362,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「仁」生多少個10年？ 洛賓證實季後離隊","createTime":"2018-12-02T16:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T17:29:00.000Z","uid":199590,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d00bfe0c5095d0d8311125ba3fc4ef5834bb9f0e","tid":925362,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"效力拜仁慕尼黑長達10季的荷蘭長青樹洛賓，周日宣佈季後會離開這支德甲班霸。<br />\n<br />\n34歲的洛賓向Omnisport證實，今季會是他在拜仁的最後一季：「這是我在拜仁的最後一年，我在這裏擁有美好的10年，現在是時候離開了。」<br />\n洛賓於2009年夏天由皇家馬德里來投，在這10年間替拜仁贏得7座德甲及4座德國盃錦標，而事業最高峯一季，便是在2012/13球季替球隊捧走歐聯，而那年對多蒙特的決賽，更由他射入2:1的奠勝球，成為球會最關鍵的捧盃功臣。<br />\n洛賓於德甲共上陣198場賽事，射入98球，而今季因膝傷問題，13輪聯賽只曾7次正選披甲。球會近年與他續約的政策，都是一年一簽，但主席漢尼斯早前在記招曾暗示，他與另一老將列貝利，季後都可能會離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181203/58984853\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58984853&d=1udu5iyFiETkxFLtB4NSTzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0fd6a343\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58984853&h=dd1e1d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20181203/58984853</a>"},{"pid":"f37feb63270a12344d3693e470791da59eaf2ec4","tid":925362,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"81fc8dbdf524dc26f391cf4d143b164d53d1f7ec","tid":925362,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:58:00.000Z","msg":"單丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66821a13804e24ddaa2fda89e253ac7a455f11bf","tid":925362,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"美職吧"},{"pid":"d05ad38791541e2b322a46765d